</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="32">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhao-zi-hua-80" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhao-zi-hua-80" class="zg-link" title="赵自华">赵自华</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ban-jiang-han" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ban-jiang-han" class="zg-link" title="半江寒">半江寒</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$kommas" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/kommas" class="zg-link" title="kommas">kommas</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


